data.description: 3BR | 2BA | 1269SQFT, charming single-family brick home.  This cozy residence features three spacious bedrooms and two bathrooms, providing ample space for comfortable living.  The property also include an attached garage, ensuring convenient and easy access for vehicle.  The classic brick exterior adds a touch of elegance and durability to the home's overall appeal.  Located in a desirable neighborhood, this property offers a great opportunity for those seeking a cozy and inviting place to call home.  Don't miss out on the chance to make this home yours.  Price is $134.5 Thousand.
